      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;[11/03/23]&lt;/strong&gt; Nominated by the CSE division for the 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.twosigma.com/community/academic-partnerships/graduate-students/phd-fellowships/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Two Sigma PhD Fellowships&lt;/a&gt; (2023-2024 Cycle).
&lt;strong&gt;[10/28/23]&lt;/strong&gt; Our short paper on 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://openreview.net/attachment?id=JIrTIMI5Yd&amp;amp;name=pdf&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Observatory Library&lt;/a&gt; accepted to the 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://table-representation-learning.github.io&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;NeurIPS TRL workshop&lt;/a&gt;.
&lt;strong&gt;[01/10/23]&lt;/strong&gt; Presented 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://arxiv.org/abs/2212.14155v2&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;WarpGate&lt;/a&gt; at the Mövenpick hotel on the waterfront of the Amsterdam city center.
&lt;strong&gt;[10/28/22]&lt;/strong&gt; Our paper 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://arxiv.org/abs/2212.14155v2&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;WarpGate&lt;/a&gt; accepted to 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.cidrdb.org/cidr2023/index.html&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;CIDR 2023&lt;/a&gt;.
&lt;strong&gt;[05/31/22]&lt;/strong&gt; Passed the PhD preliminary exam and the candidacy qualification.
&lt;strong&gt;[05/23/22]&lt;/strong&gt; Started my research internship at 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.sigmacomputing.com&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Sigma Computing&lt;/a&gt;. Many thanks to 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.madelonhulsebos.com&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Madelon Hulsebos&lt;/a&gt; for connecting me to this opportunity.
&lt;strong&gt;[04/22/22]&lt;/strong&gt; Awarded Rackham Doctoral Intern Fellowship.
&lt;strong&gt;[04/15/21]&lt;/strong&gt; Elected to the Beta Epsilon Chapter of Eta Kappa Nu (
&lt;a href=&#34;https://hkn.eecs.umich.edu&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;HKN&lt;/a&gt;).
&lt;strong&gt;[08/31/20]&lt;/strong&gt; Started my PhD at UM.&lt;/p&gt;
